title: Neither the hero we need, nor deserve

replies.body:
No wonder Teemo likes torturing melees. He's just trying to get revenge against the swordsman who killed his parents.

Also, this skin made me think of a Poison Ivy Trist. The further details of that thought would probably drive my normalcy into question.
Tell me about it, it sounds interesting!
Let's just say, if Trist is Poison Ivy, then Teemo was right about size and we know where one of the Robins came from.
I'm a little confused as to why you didn't just go with "Batmo".
